| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1572 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5c83bd18-5fd2-5d50-97a3-ffb4db9c3f89"
